name: Limited Edition Logo Hat
description:
For beautiful....for spacious skies...these EXTREMELY limited edition (11 total) AuFtr logo hats are done up right in 'Merica colors just in time for Memorial Day. These premium FlexFit hats fit fantastically well and will protect* your head from the sun, bird doodies, falling pine cones/coconuts and various other head maladies while you're going outside (it starts today).

For those fitted cap aficionados out there, our resident 59Fifty addict Bret (17 and counting) was pleasantly surprised with the high quality of these FlexFits and assures you that you'll be satisified. The L-XL fits his 7 3/4 melon even though it's labeled as only up to 7 5/8.

Get 'em while they're hot!




*Protection guarantee not legally binding. C'mon, it's a hat.

Small-Medium ships 1-2 weeks.

name: White on Heather Green Logo Shirt (Women's)
description:
We here at AuFtr have decided that our logo shirts look pretty sweet. So we want to keep the sweetness coming. We have decided to release super cool and exclusive colorways occasionally to keep you, our valued customers looking fresh. White on heather green felt appropriate for the impending holidays. Printed on soft 4.8oz, preshrunk recycled polyester, organic cotton blended tees, our women's tee will not chafe, rub or burn your delicate lady skin. 

And don't ever forget, this shirt helps. Fifty percent of our profit from the purchase will go directly to charity.
